    finger23_link : 食指橡胶垫   (rigidly attached to finger22_link)
    finger33_link : 中指橡胶垫   (rigidly attached to finger32_link)
    finger43_link : 无名指橡胶垫 (rigidly attached to finger42_link)
    finger53_link : 小拇指橡胶垫 (rigidly attached to finger52_link)

  ── Equality 多项式说明 ──────────────────────────────────────
  原始公式 (单位: 角度°):
    大拇指:  y = -0.0008x² + 0.929x  - 0.8639
    食指:    y =  0.0067x² + 0.8847x + 2.1926
    中指:    y =  0.0076x² + 0.8485x + 2.0597
    无名指:  y =  0.0079x² + 0.8321x + 2.4732
    小拇指:  y =  0.0075x² + 0.7349x + 2.0181

  MuJoCo polycoef 换算 (单位: 弧度 rad):
    y_deg = C0 + C1*x_deg + C2*x_deg²
    y_rad = C0*(π/180) + C1*x_rad + C2*(180/π)*x_rad²
    polycoef = "C0*(π/180)  C1  C2*(180/π)  0  0"
-->

